id: pm-v8fy
title: linked-test-adapters package install loses ESM module type
description: "Temp tarball smoke found that project-installed linked-test-adapters copies ESM .js extension files without a local package.json, so Node treats them as CommonJS and test-runs remains unavailable."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: agent-ux,"area:packages","area:testing"
created_at: "2026-06-18T19:08:11.244Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-18T19:15:24.880Z"
author: codex-gpt5
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: Preserved ESM semantics for copied linked-test-adapters extension installs by shipping local package metadata with the extension payload.
expected_result: Installing linked-test-adapters into a temp project makes the test-runs command family available without Node CommonJS/ESM load failures.
actual_result: "Temp tarball smoke installed linked-test-adapters, package doctor passed, test-runs status returned the background run, and copied-extension import regression coverage passed."
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-18T19:08:11.244Z",codex-gpt5,"Duplicate check: searched all pm items for linked-test-adapters CommonJS/ES module/test-runs unknown command and found no canonical open item; this is an adjacent package-platform bug discovered during pm-mcxr manual smoke."
  "2026-06-18T19:14:58.270Z",codex-gpt5,"Evidence: fixed copied linked-test-adapters installs by adding local ESM package metadata, added regression coverage for importing the copied extension entry, verified package linked test and temp tarball smoke with installed linked-test-adapters/test-runs status."
